text.textblock: Notice is hereby given that the following applicants have filed with the Federal Maritime Commission applications for licenses as ocean freight forwarders pursuant to section 19 of the Shipping Act of 1984 (46 U.S.C. app. 1718 and 46 CFR part 510).

Persons knowing of any reason why any of the following applicants should not receive a license are requested to contact the Office of Freight Forwarders, Federal Maritime Commission, Washington, DC 20573.

E.R. Hawthorne & Co., Inc., 9370 Wallisville Rd., suite 100, Houston, TX 77013. Officers: John E. Guida, President/Director, Charles B. Dorf, Vice President/Director, Charles M. Schayer, Secretary/Director
